":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:40:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ef7bdf35e5a641fdd67f3f5cc12422955cae5ef","tid":1757653,"uid":265524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<br />\n議會公開可以考慮埋比旁聽公眾發言"},{"pid":"e0803549cfe6b86ed7cc3c20e5b2de82f32214b7","tid":1757653,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3097757defddba01f2a996d129d2a5e2e2d1e84","tid":1757653,"uid":85425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:39:35.000Z","msg":"推比區議員佢地睇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:43:43.000Z","msg":"議員可能未必睇連登，可能要大家share俾自己區個議員睇下有無野係啱自己區"},{"pid":"7f68fad27823d3280c3feb3eb869411c6deb95c3","tid":1757653,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"收集左啲建議po<br />\n借位放一放喺度<br />\n<br />\n[文宣戰線, 手足請入] 建立網上區議員聯絡名冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756363\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756363</a><br />\n<br />\n陳偉業: 新議員應翻查「區議會」昔日數簿, 很可能有貪污罪證<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1754197\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1754197</a><br />\n<br />\n區政提議：所有議辦都要免費幫公公婆婆整電話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1757357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1757357</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突發 - 騎牆派選民因為咁而轉軚撐建制派!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1757451\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1757451</a><br />\n<br />\n[區政改革] 由17區議會主導創立「公民社區投票」及「公民眾籌」制度，下而上改革社區環境，實現直接民主規劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1757243\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1757243</a><br />\n<br />\n對所有區議員建議: 舉辦針對新移民嘅廣東話訓練班<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1755952\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1755952</a><br />\n<br />\n(區議會準區議員入）搞免費一日遊 (做實事）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1753920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1753920</a><br />\n<br />\n連接十八區單車徑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756592\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756592</a><br />\n<br />\n［還區議於民］區議會可唔可以搞過海隧道增加單車行通道<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756682</a>"},{"pid":"a98945028037e20c701050862059ddcd041c7eac","tid":1757653,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"太多，要set 長中短期目標，首先定上任後100日目標，要比居民知道同埋接受監察"},{"pid":"2e2cbf26c60738d456e9d0d81409b178d988e499","tid":1757653,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ef7bdf35e5a641fdd67f3f5cc12422955cae5ef","tid":1757653,"uid":265524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:43:25.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<br />\n議會公開可以考慮埋比旁聽公眾發言"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:47:37.000Z","msg":"收到，我加埋落去先"},{"pid":"fa6c14a23998076758c1e5b5cef441bd53c67d71","tid":1757653,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a98945028037e20c701050862059ddcd041c7eac","tid":1757653,"uid":283021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:47:05.000Z","msg":"太多，要set 長中短期目標，首先定上任後100日目標，要比居民知道同埋接受監察"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:56:07.000Z","msg":"同意，所以要揀嚟做，趁未正式上任就要plan定做邊D啲，值唔值得做同點做。"},{"pid":"2c8dd32402736ff518da0f535d1dd125e60eabc2","tid":1757653,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T15:59:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35bd04d8cc8d074e6a9a23acd18875b60dd8279b","tid":1757653,"uid":283424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:02:48.000Z","msg":"你講既野固然應該要做，但仲有一樣好重要既野要做先可以打破同溫層：派福利（古稱蛇齋餅粽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n啲街坊街里唔會咁有興趣理你既崇高理想，邊個有著數我咪俾我我咪撐邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"728d3e0962589177fb531186a0f8e59d569d84a0","tid":1757653,"uid":34487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0