39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d21ad657349a55cd34cc44f2e6f680fbb7f62b01","tid":1757653,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba8c50e1d673eaa917e95a4e458b621520b63d67","tid":1757653,"uid":39092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:41:54.000Z","msg":"用區議會名義搞集會突破公安條例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"要法律巴絲研究下可以點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:50:39.000Z","msg":"集會(meeting)指任何經召集或組織而舉行的聚集或集結，而該聚集或集結是以討論一般公眾人士或某一類公眾人士感興趣或關注的問題或事項為目的，或是以在該等問題或事項上表達意見為目的，並包括當中有人為以上目的而在現場負責控制或領導，或企圖為以上目的而在現場負責控制或領導的任何聚集或集結，不論此等聚集或集結事先有無經過召集或組織；但完全為以下目的而召集或組織的聚集或集結，則不包括在內 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)<br />\n為社交、康樂、文化、學術、教育、宗教或慈善目的而進行的聚集或集結，或真誠地擬為討論屬社交、康樂、文化、學術、教育、宗教、慈善、專業、業務或商務性質的論題，而以會議或研討會形式進行的聚集或集結；<br />\n(b)<br />\n為殯殮而舉行的聚集或集結；<br />\n(c)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為任何公共機構而舉行的聚集或集結；或<br />\n(d)<br />\n為執行或行使任何條例所委以或授予的職責或權力而舉行的聚集或集結</span></span>；  (由1980年第67號第2條代替)"},{"pid":"19efa819d86b7b3127f99d3ea565e6ca4bbdcdea","tid":1757653,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"40c7810c1cdd25ca6db28d8476cd3601d643c758","tid":1757653,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d21ad657349a55cd34cc44f2e6f680fbb7f62b01","tid":1757653,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba8c50e1d673eaa917e95a4e458b621520b63d67","tid":1757653,"uid":39092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:41:54.000Z","msg":"用區議會名義搞集會突破公安條例 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:49:32.000Z","msg":"要法律巴絲研究下可以點玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:50:39.000Z","msg":"集會(meeting)指任何經召集或組織而舉行的聚集或集結，而該聚集或集結是以討論一般公眾人士或某一類公眾人士感興趣或關注的問題或事項為目的，或是以在該等問題或事項上表達意見為目的，並包括當中有人為以上目的而在現場負責控制或領導，或企圖為以上目的而在現場負責控制或領導的任何聚集或集結，不論此等聚集或集結事先有無經過召集或組織；但完全為以下目的而召集或組織的聚集或集結，則不包括在內 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)<br />\n為社交、康樂、文化、學術、教育、宗教或慈善目的而進行的聚集或集結，或真誠地擬為討論屬社交、康樂、文化、學術、教育、宗教、慈善、專業、業務或商務性質的論題，而以會議或研討會形式進行的聚集或集結；<br />\n(b)<br />\n為殯殮而舉行的聚集或集結；<br />\n(c)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為任何公共機構而舉行的聚集或集結；或<br />\n(d)<br />\n為執行或行使任何條例所委以或授予的職責或權力而舉行的聚集或集結</span></span>；  (由1980年第67號第2條代替)"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:52:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200801/30/P200801300130.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F200801%2F30%2FP200801300130.htm&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx95hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=88cc0041\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/200801/30/P200801300130.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n（ii）《防止賄賂條例》（第２０１章）第４、５、６及７條專門處理涉及「公共機構」的賄賂行為，例如為了促致合約或他人撤回投標而作的賄賂。<span style=\"color: red;\">《防止賄賂條例》第2條界定「公共機構」一詞的定義為：<br />\n（a）政府；<br />\n（b）行政會議；<br />\n（c）立法會；<br />\n（d）各區議會；</span><br />\n（e）由行政長官或行政長官會同行政會議委出，或由他人代行政長官或行政長官會同行政會議委出的各類委員會或其他機構，不論該委員會或機構是否獲得酬勞；以及<br />\n（f）《防止賄賂條例》附表1指明的各類委員會或其他機構，例如香港房屋委員會、醫院管理局及機場管理局。<br />\n<br />\n政府2008年解釋過，唔知佢有無搬龍門"},{"pid":"def520ddcd6083197f041db461f5c7843d42376a","tid":1757653,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:54:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elegislation.gov.hk%2Fhk%2Fcap1&d=AiROHBMCWVTnLPrCQVkx95hbjDs%2B%2F0Yai8vOOt2IPjE%3D&h=5a1f9b99\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elegislation.gov.hk/hk/cap1</a><br />\n<br />\n公共機構<br />\n(public body)包括 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)行政會議；  (由1998年第26號第37條修訂)<br />\n(b)立法會；  (由1998年第26號第37條修訂)<br />\n(c)(由1999年第78號第7條廢除)<br />\n(ca)任何區議會；  (由1981年第42號第27條增補)<br />\n(cb)(由1999年第78號第7條廢除)<br />\n(d)任何其他市區、郊區或城市議局；<br />\n(e)任何特區政府部門；及  (由1998年第26號第37條修訂)<br />\n(f)任何由特區政府承擔的事業；  (由1998年第26號第37條修訂)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f726647b35421e3ea7e0732d9efffab54646d2b","tid":1757653,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:58:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9fc7dc93e634eb7191431f7c7e3d46f62710a0ad","tid":1757653,"uid":310700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T16:59:49.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"9be361f57f328b51aff47b78e667c9deb317e039","tid":1757653,"uid":328969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:02:43.000Z","msg":"做到野一定要有大大張poster講出來，雖然經常笑禮儀廉的成功爭取，但真係有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人係靠呢個先知你做過D咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb910fd29ee68aa88a56bc9a8f9ecca2dd83ce31","tid":1757653,"uid":269712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:09:36.000Z","msg":"下面一個建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">好多屋苑法團都曾經或而家出現<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">利益輸送, 圍標</span></span>等問題, 特別係大維修時<br />\n另外  <span style=\"color: red;\">屋苑管理公司質素</span> / 手法 / 同法團關係 /  popo擅闖屋苑管理公司應對問題 ,等等 <br />\n上面呢D 係好直接關係到當區居民對區議員係唔係做到野一個好重要指標, <br />\n如果主動出席居民大會以監察者角色跟進大會, 有律師在場更好 <br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ebdc20a95c83ceed5738049fde2fd3a53e481a23","tid":1757653,"uid":201464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T17:42:17.000Z","msg":"<ins></ins>"},{"pid":"ad7c8d18c3beedda8c8d504f8725f7339ada239a","tid":1757653,"uid":16864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:13:02.000Z","msg":"追究7 21"},{"pid":"1bf1d893fa1c574eab41b3ad0900a948a763e257","tid":1757653,"uid":212246,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T19:37:06.000Z","msg":"要俾多D街坊福利搶埋建制派剩低嘅票<br />\n1. 免費小學功課輔導班/英文班/數學班/興趣班<br />\n人手方面可以招讀緊大學嘅手足義教，拎綜援/關愛基金生活嘅家庭或單親家庭優先。手足同學生家長要不時一齊講下小朋友嘅學習情況，班師奶同義教手足熟咗嘅話可以提高埋立法會選舉嘅得票率<br />\n2. 中學義務私補配對<br />\n幫拎綜援/關愛基金生活嘅家庭或單親家庭嘅中學生同讀緊大學嘅手足做配對，逢星期六日幫手上門/去社區中心私補<br />\n3. 社區瑜伽班<br />\n4. 定期為老人家提供量血壓、認知功能測試<br />\n5. 每個區議員整番個whatsapp channel，直接向街坊宣傳有D咩活動/福利順便放多D real news<br />\n6. 社區中心聖誕party<br />\n7. 新移民粵語班/勞工法例講座<br />\n仲有，油尖旺區嘅陳梓維你真係要請到一team人幫手先得。"},{"pid":"a3c4993d6d731e30cfcc3460becd410284f79d4f","tid":1757653,"uid":283318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T21:18:14.000Z","msg":"推啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186b9ac74e64e90080db74f9588951f299982cee","tid":1757653,"uid":43009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:45:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872e035d5ce8136ffaeb1c1486db956d980c34fe","tid":1757653,"uid":190295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T00:51:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00164d25dd50bab2961260a376cf1dd8258cfbf","tid":1757653,"uid":10131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"